<plot>Based on the critically acclaimed stage play, 'Murder by Appointment' focuses on the Langford family, with parents Joan and Richard returning from a dinner dance late at night, during a heavy storm. Eldest son David has been at home all night and younger son Charles has taken a girl back to her home after the dance. Soon, a body is discovered and the family begin to question each other's whereabouts during the course of the evening.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?381854</url></doc>
